OL,3,CMeghan records MasterChef Australia
OL,4,Cshow as she focuses on business
OL,5,Cventures
OL,7,FMeghan used the second day of the
OL,8,Fcouple's tour to promote her
OL,9,Fcommercial ventures, while Prince
OL,10,FHarry was on a more traditional visit,
OL,11,Ftalking about men's mental health, as
OL,12,FITV News Royal Editor Chris Ship
OL,13,Fexplains
OL,15,FThe debate about the royal, not-royal
OL,16,Ftour upon which the Duke and Duchess
OL,17,Fof Sussex have embarked in Australia
OL,18,Fhas been intense.
OL,20,FIs this a copy of their 2018 visit
OL,21,Fwhen they were working Royals?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776287489
OL,3,CMeghan records MasterChef Australia
OL,4,Cshow as she focuses on business
OL,5,Cventures
OL,7,FShould they be doing it in a country
OL,8,Fwhich is still a Commonwealth Realm
OL,9,Fwhere King Charles remains Head of
OL,10,FState?
OL,12,FAre they blurring the lines between
OL,13,Ftheir philanthropic work and their
OL,14,Fcommercial ventures?
OL,16,FAre Australian taxpayers footing the
OL,17,Fbill for the security the Sussexes
OL,18,Frequire in many of the places they go?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776287489
OL,3,CMeghan records MasterChef Australia
OL,4,Cshow as she focuses on business
OL,5,Cventures
OL,7,FYou won't be surprised to learn that
OL,8,Fviews on this issue are as divided as
OL,9,Fthey always are when it comes to Harry
OL,10,Fand Meghan, both in the UK and in
OL,11,FAustralia.
OL,13,FAnd inevitably, many media
OL,14,Forganisations are simply lining up in
OL,15,Ftheir traditional lanes to either
OL,16,Fsupport or to tear apart the Duke and
OL,17,FDuchess.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776287489
OL,3,CMeghan records MasterChef Australia
OL,4,Cshow as she focuses on business
OL,5,Cventures
OL,7,FBut for a couple who were clear about
OL,8,Ftheir intentions to be 'financially
OL,9,Findependent' after moving to
OL,10,FCalifornia, this trip is a bit of a
OL,11,Fmasterstroke.
OL,13,FFor Meghan, Australia is a country in
OL,14,Fwhich she intends to expand her As
OL,15,FEver business.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776287489
OL,3,CMeghan records MasterChef Australia
OL,4,Cshow as she focuses on business
OL,5,Cventures
OL,7,FThe brand, which famously sells jam,
OL,8,Fflower sprinkles and rose wine, is
OL,9,Fcurrently only available to consumers
OL,10,Fin the USA, and the Duchess wants to
OL,11,Ftake it to a new English-speaking
OL,12,Fmarket.
OL,14,FSo, her appearance on MasterChef
OL,15,FAustralia makes perfect sense when her
OL,16,FAs Ever brand is all about food, drink
OL,17,Fand entertaining.
OL,26,@pD@Yrr
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
