CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776287489
OL,3,CMeghan records MasterChef Australia
OL,4,Cshow as she focuses on business
OL,5,Cventures
OL,7,FA spokesperson for MasterChef said she
OL,8,Ffeatured as "a guest judge on the
OL,9,Fcountry's most beloved cooking show"
OL,10,Fon which she "mentored and guided"
OL,11,Fcontestants alongside the regular
OL,12,Fjudges Poh Ling Yeow, Sofia Levin and
OL,13,FJean-Christophe Novelli.
OL,15,FIt will air on the Channel 10 network
OL,16,Fon 19 April.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
