CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776287489
OL,3,CMeghan records MasterChef Australia
OL,4,Cshow as she focuses on business
OL,5,Cventures
OL,7,FMeghan recorded the episode at TV
OL,8,Fstudios in Melbourne on Wednesday,
OL,9,Fwhile Harry carried out a more
OL,10,Ftraditional visit to the city's
OL,11,FAustralian rules club, the Western
OL,12,FBulldogs.
OL,14,FHe spoke about men's mental health, as
OL,15,Fwell as his own, with the charity
OL,16,FMovember.
OL,18,FIt had a strong whiff of a traditional
OL,19,Froyal engagement about it.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
