OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776287489
OL,3,CMeghan records MasterChef Australia
OL,4,Cshow as she focuses on business
OL,5,Cventures
OL,7,FMeghan's activity on Wednesday,
OL,8,Fmeanwhile, was purely commercial.
OL,10,FThe outfit she wore to record the
OL,11,FMasterChef episode has already been
OL,12,Fuploaded to a website which promotes
OL,13,Fthe clothes celebrities wear.
OL,15,FWednesday's clothing choices were from
OL,16,Fthe Australian brand Matteau and are
OL,17,Flisted on the website OneOff, where
OL,18,Fthe Duchess is also an investor.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
