PN,30409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776287489
OL,3,CMeghan records MasterChef Australia
OL,4,Cshow as she focuses on business
OL,5,Cventures
OL,7,FThe silk shirt is priced at #390, the
OL,8,Fskirt at #480 and the shoes (Manolo
OL,9,FBlahnik) at #530.
OL,11,FTotal cost: #1,400.
OL,13,FTuesday's two outfits are also listed,
OL,14,Fshould anyone wish to copy her style.
OL,16,FThe dress (Australian designer Karen
OL,17,FGee), plus earrings and shoes
OL,18,F(Christian Dior) that she wore to a
OL,19,Fchildren's hospital and homeless
OL,20,Fshelter in Melbourne, cost a total of
OL,21,F#1,580.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
