FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776287489
OL,3,CMeghan records MasterChef Australia
OL,4,Cshow as she focuses on business
OL,5,Cventures
OL,7,FOther Australian labels were worn for
OL,8,Fanother visit on Tuesday. The St Agni
OL,9,Fand P. Johnson combination is listed
OL,10,Fon OneOff as costing #2,110.
OL,12,FBy investing in the website as well as
OL,13,Fprofiting from any uplift in sales
OL,14,Ffrom the clothes she wears, Meghan is
OL,15,Fshowing herself to be a sharp
OL,16,Fbusinesswoman who is happy to
OL,17,Fcapitalise on the attention her
OL,18,Foutfits will inevitably get.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
