OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1776287489
OL,3,CMeghan records MasterChef Australia
OL,4,Cshow as she focuses on business
OL,5,Cventures
OL,7,FHarry and Meghan's office says the
OL,8,Fcouple wanted to visit organisations
OL,9,Fthat "align with their interests and
OL,10,Fvalues", but their staff do
OL,11,Facknowledge that the four-day visit to
OL,12,FAustralia does have "broader
OL,13,Fcommercial" objectives.
OL,15,FIt is not, their office makes clear, a
OL,16,F"royal tour".
OL,18,FThis is the Talking Royals - our
OL,19,Fweekly podcast about the Royal Family,
OL,20,Fwith ITV News Royal Editor Chris Ship
OL,21,Fand Producer Lizzie Robinson.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/12
